@NODE MPNewProject "Menu: Project.NewProject"
@PREV "MainMenuProject"
@TOC "ManualMenus"

Clears the actual project. The Picture, Map-Buffer, Flip-Table, Brush-
Table will be removed from memory!!
@ENDNODE

@NODE MPLoad "Menu: Project.Load"
@TOC "ManualMenus"

@{" Project ... " LINK ""}
@{" Picture ... " LINK ""}
@{" Map ...     " LINK ""}

Makes appear a File-Requester to load a Project, Picture or Map-File de-
pending on the Sub-Menu you have selected!
@ENDNODE

@NODE MPSave "Menu: Project.Save"
@TOC "ManualMenus"

@{" Project ... " LINK ""}
@{" Map ...     " LINK ""}

Makes appear a File-Requester to save the actual Project or Map-Buffer de-
pending on the Sub-Menu you have selected!
@ENDNODE

@NODE MPEditMap "Menu: Project.Edit Map"
@TOC "ManualMenus"

Enters the @{" Edit-Mode " LINK "ManualEditingMaps"}! Will fail if there's no picture in memory!
@ENDNODE

@NODE MPInfo "Menu: Project.Information"
@TOC "ManualMenus"

Brings up an Info-Requester!
@ENDNODE

@NODE MPIconify "Menu: Project.Iconify"
@TOC "ManualMenus"

Iconifies PowerCrawler.
@ENDNODE

@NODE MPQuit "Menu: Project.Quit"
@NEXT "MainMenuProject"
@TOC "ManualMenus"

Quits the program. Deletes also the temporary Project-Files in T: See
@{" Tooltypes " LINK "TTKillPrjBuffers"} if you don't want this Files to be deleted!
@ENDNODE

